sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Web as Next.js UI
    participant Wallet as Solana Wallet
    participant Nonce as POST /api/auth/nonce
    participant Verify as POST /api/auth/verify
    participant Auth as walletAuth service
    participant DB as MongoDB users

    User->>Web: Open /
    User->>Wallet: Connect wallet
    Web->>Nonce: walletAddress
    Nonce->>Auth: createWalletNonce(walletAddress, domain)
    Auth-->>Nonce: nonce, message, expiresAt
    Nonce-->>Web: Signable message
    Web->>Wallet: signMessage(message)
    Wallet-->>Web: signature
    Web->>Verify: walletAddress, message, signature
    Verify->>Auth: verifyWalletSignature(domain, message, signature)
    Auth-->>Verify: walletAddress
    Verify->>DB: findOne({ walletAddress })
    DB-->>Verify: existing user or null
    Verify->>Auth: createSession(walletAddress, userId)
    Auth-->>Verify: session token and expiresAt
    Verify-->>Web: user, requiresOnboarding, Set-Cookie
    alt Existing completed profile
        Web->>Web: route to /overview
    else Missing profile data
        Web->>Web: route to /onboarding
    end
